# Copy to .env.local — never commit real values.
# As of today the public iconsol app does not require any env vars to run
# locally. This file is a placeholder so future contributors know where
# to put new keys.

# Example (uncomment when added):
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=
# RATE_LIMIT_TOKENS_PER_MINUTE=60
